{"tid":907523,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中美洲難民軍侵襲美國，試圖攀越圍牆","createTime":"2018-11-19T00:27:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-20T02:41:30.000Z","uid":64191,"like":82,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"3a0e3f4bfd8f42ff2382e86bedf5da759b8f5ce0","tid":907523,"uid":64191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T00:27:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2GuuNzR_AZg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D2GuuNzR_AZg&d=pZBVOThsalqHuy22W8pBzKWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=05bb9d8d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2GuuNzR_AZg</a><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jjiAUsobpTU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DjjiAUsobpTU&d=pZBVOThsalqHuy22W8pBzKWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=96181cee\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jjiAUsobpTU</a><br />\n<br />\n暫時未有任何主流媒體報導，但已經有片見到，上面段片應該係加州邊境，一班難民攀爬邊境圍牆，與美國既人對峙<br />\n<br />\n即使墨西哥願意收留，但大多數難民堅持前往美國，就如昔日既哥德人一樣<br />\n<br />\n歷史教訓：羅馬帝國後期，受匈人入侵而被迫離開家園既哥德人，大舉前往羅馬帝國邊境尋求庇護，後來羅馬安置佢地，更收編部分哥德人做軍隊作戰<br />\n<br />\n然而，當哥德人逗留日久，滲入做羅馬既軍隊後，隨著原來羅馬既墮落，哥德人趁亂殺入羅馬，響亞平寧半島、西歐一帶四處侵略，直接導致西羅馬帝國滅亡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b77b6497c0c0f4c406423d8ba070dc866074a39d","tid":907523,"uid":166474,"like":0,"dislike":16,"score":-16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T00:28:44.000Z","msg":"開槍囉笨柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"406c9ff0d2e21c685dce221eb019f782c74df86f","tid":907523,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T00:32:47.000Z","msg":"大種乞衣"},{"pid":"7a00eb21197cbef0076551b169786ea11f7240ea","tid":907523,"uid":64191,"like":24,"dislike":