l/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你一用大殺傷力武器炸平民，一比人見到影到，國內成班一齊反你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n越南戰爭就係咁，比國內左膠抗爭成功，越南就靠人海戰術趕走美軍<br />\n<br />\n除非演變到國仇家恨，唔係人海戰術對美國都會好有用"},{"pid":"f9c525bdba7246128847fb2c0acdd8fd8fef125f","tid":907523,"uid":11148,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3a0e3f4bfd8f42ff2382e86bedf5da759b8f5ce0","tid":907523,"uid":64191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T00:27:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2GuuNzR_AZg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D2GuuNzR_AZg&d=pZBVOThsalqHuy22W8pBzKWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=05bb9d8d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2GuuNzR_AZg</a><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jjiAUsobpTU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DjjiAUsobpTU&d=pZBVOThsalqHuy22W8pBzKWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=96181cee\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jjiAUsobpTU</a><br />\n<br />\n暫時未有任何主流媒體報導，但已經有片見到，上面段片應該係加州邊境，一班難民攀爬邊境圍牆，與美國既人對峙<br />\n<br />\n即使墨西哥願意收留，但大多數難民堅持前往美國，就如昔日既哥德人一樣<br />\n<br />\n歷史教訓：羅馬帝國後期，受匈人入侵而被迫離開家園既哥德人，大舉前往羅馬帝國邊境尋求庇護，後來羅馬安置佢地，更收編部分哥德人做軍隊作戰<br />\n<br />\n然而，當哥德人逗留日久，滲入做羅馬既軍隊後，隨著原來羅馬既墮落，哥德人趁亂殺入羅馬，響亞平寧半島、西歐一帶四處侵略，直接導致西羅馬帝國滅亡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T04:46:38.000Z","msg":"近代都有羅興亞人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bc80d3b251e245e703436302413fbc7eb2fb96c","tid":907523,"uid":57376,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"b0888e2ed3b3467e35975f42b3ac5b87205393ab","tid":90